Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, menu
Recommends: hwinfo
Package: grub-customizer
Description: Grub Customizer - A graphical Grub2/BURG configuration application
 Grub Customizer is a graphical interface to configure the grub2/burg settings
 with focus on the individual list order - without losing the dynamical
 behavior of grub - also usable on live cds.
 Settings like the background or timeouts are also changeable using
 Grub Customizer.
